title: AWESOME HOME NEAR DENVER UNIVERSITY AND PORTER HOSPITAL!
app_fee: $40.00 application fee for credit/criminal background checks and processing
posting_body: ['AWESOME home at corner of Williams Street and Yale Avenue!', 'Available for August 1st occupancy!', 'Great location near the University of Denver and Porter Hospital!', 'Nice fireplace in the living room and lustrous hardwood floors throughout the main level.', 'In the kitchen this lovely home features granite countertops, stainless-steel kitchen appliances (refrigerator, electric range, dishwasher, microwave, and sink!', 'Three bedrooms and two bathrooms total -- the upstairs features two bedrooms, one full bathroom, living room with fireplace, dining room, and lovely kitchen.', 'Downstairs is finished with a third bedroom, a family room, a large laundry room WITH WASHER & DRYER INCLUDED, full bathroom, and extra storage rooms!', 'Covered front and back porches ideal for relaxing and entertaining!', '1-car detached garage with automatic door opener, plus you get two more off-street parking spaces next to garage!', 'Fenced backyard.', 'No smoking.', '$40.00 non-refundable application fee.', 'Small pets may be acceptable with pet deposit and pet rent.', '**ON INITIAL CONTACT PLEASE PROVIDE BASIC INFORMATION ABOUT ALL PERSONS TO LIVE IN HOME, TYPE OF EMPLOYMENT, PETS IF ANY, AND DESIRED MOVE-IN DATE!', 'University of Denver, Denver University, DU, near college, Yale, Porter Hospital']
